RAW INSTALLAION INSTRUCTIONS
============================

1) Become root

2) cd /

3) tar zxvf ntoscript_<version>.tar.gz

INSTALLED FILES AND DIRECTORIES
===============================

INSTALL (this file)
usr/bin/ntoscript
usr/share/doc/ntoscript/
usr/share/doc/ntoscript/userman.pdf
usr/share/ntoscript/scripts/
usr/share/ntoscript/scripts/tutorial*.fs
usr/share/ntoscript/scripts/xephem.fs


DEPENDENCIES
============

This package depends on:
  libc.so (>= libc.so.6)
  libz.so (>= libz.so.1.2.3)
  libmpeparser.so.0 
Except for libmpeparser.so.0, they are probally installed on your system.
You can get  libmpeparser.so.0 at

ftp://public:@soton.mpeforth.com/libmpeparser_3.0b-3_i386.deb

LAST MINUTE
===========

Type 'ntoscript' to check the instalation.
